text: pitabrakd nasa puok del brachheang nung bantoul robsa yeung yeung nung banhchoul puokke tow knong phleung nork . real pel del sbek robsa puokke ban cheh khlaoch asa yeung kaban btau r sbek phe sa ng tiet aoy puokke daembi aoy puokke ttuol rosacheate tearounakamm . pitabrakd nasa a l laoh mha khlangpouke mha ktebandet
